{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"29ee91d11c","title":"关于加强学校思想政治工作问题给周恩来等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d59c236e84","index":0,"year":1957,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"29ee91d11c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"34cc128e8c","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"29ee91d11c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。彭真，当时任中共中央书记处书记。定一，即陆定一，当时任中共中央宣传部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6050db84f8","type":"title","text":"关于加强学校思想政治工作问题给周恩来等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"29ee91d11c"},{"id":"34cc128e8c","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来、陈云、彭真、定一同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"29ee91d11c"},{"id":"a8283ffa43","type":"paragraph","text":"大学、中学都要求加强思想、政治领导和改进思想、政治教育，要削减课程，要恢复中学方面的政治课，取消宪治（法）课，要编新的思想、政治课本，要下决心从党政两系统抽调几批得力而义适宜于做学校工作的+部去天、中学校工作，要赋予高等教育部和教育部以领导思想政治工作的任务。以上各点，请中央讨论一次，并作出决定。我已到天津。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"29ee91d11c"},{"id":"e4d25d5498","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"29ee91d11c"},{"id":"81df12d745","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年三月十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"29ee91d11c"}],"page":{"id":"47fba79ba7","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"29ee91d11c","start":424,"end":424}}}},"__N_SSG":true}